## Standardized assessment and appeals

The rate of foster care payment should be determined using the standardized assessment tool: 

- First, within 40 calendar days of placement, AND at least every 6 months after the first assessment, or 
- In the event of significant change in circumstances

You will receive written notification of the payment rate after a standardized assessment is completed. You have a right to request departmental review based on information that was not considered in the assessment. You can also initiate a process to request a department review.

